{"tid":239303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"容海恩承認用真名玩Clash Royale，仲係個盟副首領","createTime":"2017-05-11T14:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T05:53:24.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"efcfa612e5d9c4f01d621db73d358670063b93b0","tid":239303,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T14:43:14.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】新民黨立法會議員容海恩（Eunice）嘅口才大家都見識過，原來佢天性「宅女」，私底下好鍾意打機。最近Eunice迷上一個好出名嘅手遊「Clash Royale（部落衝突）」，仲唔驚現真身，拎真名出嚟行走江湖，佢都話，有網民向佢親自求證，係咪「真．容海恩」。Emily望過，Eunice喺個遊戲升級得好快，喺一個叫「港男港女聯盟」團隊中做埋副首領，唔知有無網民同佢交過手？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係機迷，不過Eunice先旨聲明，自己從來無喺議會廳開會時玩過，佢仲堅稱唔會畀錢玩，話因為呢啲嘢真係返唔到轉頭㗎。其實除咗Eunice之外，議會內香港眾志羅冠聰都係出咗名鍾意打機，仲有「電競聰」嘅花名。唔知兩個人之後係咪都可以跨黨派聯手，推動香港嘅電競產業發展呢？"},{"pid":"62b1559ce52542cac88cd07da5a52078d49cb81e","tid":239303,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T01:43:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75802567a9d543833fe982a5bf5dd6445412956","tid":239303,"uid":4493,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T02:31:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾人玩垃圾game"},{"pid":"54038b16ec4a8a28caa4fe858458267c5a24ecb7","tid":239303,"uid":1082,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T02:32:35.000Z","msg":"佢唯一既才能就係呢樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694417637d6be6b54d4ad527ec2ff9f88853ee14","tid":239303,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T02:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5de9e90b92d11d19cabc03d29e1082e409a6e848","tid":239303,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"屌&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/